
LUDO

 - player
  - color (yellow|green|red|blue)
  - pieces (array)
  - startField (field id)
  + setName
  + allPiecesAtHome (true|false)

 - piece
  - position (field id)
  - count (how far is the piece on the board)
  - cx (integer)
  - cy (integer)
  + moveOrdinary (new field attr)
  + moveFromHome (startField attr)
  + moveFinal (final field attr)
  + goHome (home base field attr)
  + setX (set the cx)
  + setY (set the cy)
  + setPosition (set the position)

 - dice
  - numbers (array)
  + throwDice (integer)

 - diceNumber
  - number (integer)
  - textNumber (name)
